6. Warranty and Liability Disclaimer
Refer to the warranty and liability disclaimers outlined in the MIT License section.

7. Termination of License
Violation of any terms in this agreement may result in termination of your license to use NOWA-Engine.
Upon termination, all rights granted by this license will be revoked, and you must cease using NOWA-Engine immediately.

8. Contact Information
